hough it is less common, but <a href=\"http://europepmc.org/abstract/MED/11677423\" rel=\"nofollow\">bacteria may cause haepatitis<\/a>.<\/p>\n","answer_id":23392,"question_id":23239,"up_vote_count":1,"last_edit_date":1450144684}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/23239/can-hepatitis-be-caused-by-bacteria","last_activity_date":1450144684,"creation_date":1413550083,"answer_count":2,"title":"Can Hepatitis be caused by Bacteria?","body":"<p>There are many information about viral hepatitis. But it is interesting for me, can bacteria cause the hepatitis too?<\/p>\n","question_id":23239,"tags":["human-biology","bacteriology","hepatitis"],"score":4,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":136,"up_vote_count":4,"last_edit_date":1413786301},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/28273af7cc50bb66fb34cd0f71c19988?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"unregistered","user_id":20640,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/20640/user20640","reputation":6,"display_name":"user20640"},"closed_date":1450184698,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/476e67c92121154e7910301e56cdfc4c?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":948,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/948/mattdmo","reputation":7591,"display_name":"MattDMo","accept_rate":50},"score":0,"post_id":41531,"edited":false,"creation_date":1450140291,"comment_id":70466,"body":"Please <a href=\"http://biology.stackexchange.com/posts/41531/edit\">edit<\/a> your question to provide some examples, as well as your own thinking on this topic. Homework and school-related questions are off-topic on Biology unless you&#39;ve shown your attempt at an answer. For more information see our <a href=\"http://biology.stackexchange.com/help/homework\">homework policy<\/a>."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/1YczA.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":9943,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/9943/c